data.description: Discover a captivating 4-bedroom (with possible 5th in the basement), 3.5-bathroom home in the picturesque Moline area. This gem rests upon a sprawling wooded lot, providing both privacy and natural beauty. Step onto the deck or patio to soak in the tranquility and connect with nature. The heart of the home is a spacious kitchen adorned with an inviting island, perfect for culinary adventures and gatherings. Unwind in the finished basement, complete with a full bathroom and 5th bedroom with a convenient walkout. Plus, the added surprise of a miniature kitchen enhances the basement's functionality. Experience the perfect fusion of comfort, nature, and convenience in this remarkable residence.
